WELKOM K9 Unit members were en-route to Odendaalsrus for an operation when they members saw a motorist walking along the R30 road between Welkom and Odendaalsrus on Friday, 15 July. Cops approached him and upon close inspection and questioning, they found drugs such as CAT, Chrystal Meth and Tik in the container near his car. The man (39) was bust for possession of drugs. He will appear in the Welkom Magistrates Court soon.